description: Starbreeze AB engages in the creation, publication and distribution of entertainment products. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 133 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2000-07-31. The company specializes in the action and adventure genre. The Company’s title portfolio includes such completed games, as Syndicate, The Chronicles of Riddick: Assault on Dark Athena, The Darkness, The Chronicles of Riddick: Escape from Butcher Bay, Knights of the Temple, Enclave and The Outforce. The firm has several subsidiaries, namely Starbreeze Studios AS, Sidecar 1 AB, Geminose Inc, Orange Grove Media, SLG Everscreen AB, Payday Productions LLC, Orange Grove Media Inc and Enterspace AB.
name: Starbreeze AB
